Frank Greene, Greg Gisbert, Randy Brecker: trumpet; 
Claudio Roditi: trumpet, percussion; 
Frank Wess, Antonio Hart: alto sax, flute; 
Jimmy Heath: tenor sax; 
James Moody: tenor sax, flute, vocals; 
Gary Smulyan: baritone sax; 
Jason Jackson, Steve Davis: trombone; 
Jay Ashby: trombone, percussion; 
Douglas Purviance: bass trombone; 
Mulgrew Miller: piano; 
Marty Ashby: guitars; 
John Lee: bass; 
Dennis Mackrel: drums; 
Roberta Gambarini: vocals. 
Special guest artist: Roy Hargrove: trumpet (3,6).

